query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('amazon-web-services',
'async-await',
'google-places-api',
'html-select',
'jax-rs',
'jvm',
'mfc',
'parallel-processing',
'screenshot',
'tcp',
'vue.js',
'webforms',
'xsd');
